questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I be able to easily modify my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, you can easily modify your website by adding a page builder plugin that will help you customize and update your content without technical knowledge. If you encounter any issues during the process, feel free to reach out to me anytime as I am available 24/7 to assist you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you convert a Figma design into a responsive WordPress website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely, I can convert your Figma design into a fully responsive WordPress website, ensuring it looks great on all devices and screen sizes.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What type of data do you need to begin working on the website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
provide me following details:
Login details for your WordPress website or hosting/cPanel.
Domain name.

questionsAndAnswers.question: If I show you a reference website that I like, can you create one similar to it?
Do you build multilingual websites?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I specialize in creating multilingual websites to help you reach a global audience.
